    "2863:15": "copaviṣṭo muktakeśo dakṣiṇābhimukho yogī mukhaprakṣiptapañcāmṛtavaṭikaḥ",
    "2863:16": "śrīheruketyakṣaracatuṣṭayasyārthamāmukhayan",
