    "2863:35": "none“> sarvasattvahitasukhahetave śrīheruko'hamiti",
    "2863:36": "triruccārya dvibhujasambaramātmānamadhimucya tadanantaram - oṃkārādi hu hu",
    "2863:37": "phaṭ mantramālikālipaṃktiṃ pañcaraśmikāṃ triruccārya pariveṣṭya sthitā",
    "2863:38": "spharanti (?) | cakre devatāvṛndamarddhitavipravṛndāṃ ( ndaṃ )",
    "2863:39": "bhāvayitvā kiṃ kartavyamityāha -",
    "2863:40": "normal;mso-pagination:",
    "2863:41": "none;mso-layout-grid-align:",
